                              hadoop-word-counter

count words and phrases in text.

hadoop is used for parsing multiple files.

usage:

  - count phrases:

    hadoop jar PhraseCounter.jar gemma.org.PhraseCounter.PhraseCounter [inputDataDirectory] [outputDataDirectory] [phrase_length]

  - count words:

    hadoop jar WordCounter.jar gemma.org.WordCounter.WordCounter [inputDataDirectory] [outputDataDirectory] ["word1" "word2" "word3" â€¦]
